You need to flat map the structure to `Stream&lt;Object&gt;` and then use the `distinct` to get the unique items. However, first, you need to convert [JSONArray to List][1].

    List&lt;String&gt; xvalues = arrayToStream(datasets)
        .map(JSONObject.class::cast)
        .map(dataset -&gt; dataset -&gt; {
