They need to be the exact same ParameterExpression instance for this to work. For that you can leverage an expression rewriter to modify one of the expressions: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.linq.expressions.expressionvisitor?view=netframework-4.8

I think you should be able to use a library like predicate builder to do the same thing in a simpler way though:

https://www.nuget.org/packages/PredicateBuilder/

